document.full_text: u-prince  - singer michel martelly won haiti's presidential election with 67.57 percent of the vote, compared with 31.74 percent for rival mirlande manigat, according to official preliminary results released on monday.
document.title: martelly wins haiti election with 67.57 percent: official
lines_and_colors: u-prince  - singer michel martelly won haiti's presidential election with 67.57 percent of the vote, compared with 31.74 percent for rival mirlande manigat, according to official preliminary results released on monday.
